trans-unit.source: Provides interconversion of managed <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> objects and unmanaged Graphics Device Interface (GDI) <see href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd183565">DEVMODE</see> structures.
trans-unit.target: 提供托管 <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintTicket" /> 对象和非托管图形设备接口 (GDI) <see href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dd183565">DEVMODE</see> 结构之间的相互转换。

trans-unit.source: This namespace is part of the enhanced printing services provided with Windows Presentation Foundation.
trans-unit.target: 此命名空间是增强打印提供的服务的 Windows Presentation Foundation 的一部分。

trans-unit.source: Managed code developers using Windows Forms must use the APIs in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 使用 Windows 窗体的托管的代码开发人员必须使用中的 Api<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空间。
